message:
How to double your agency without buying a course, getting coaching, or hiring a consultant.

Right now it seems like a gold rush to share some secret ingredient, some magic phrase, or some piece of information that transforms your agency.

Here is the problem with buying information. It’s one you know instinctively. When you figure something out, do you want to share it with others? People you may end up competing with?

Of course not!

But there is another problem you know deep down. Once you learn the “secret” and enough people use it, it stops working… Kinda like 100 guys using the same pickup line on a girl.

It might work for the first guy and maybe the second one… But after the 100th guy has used it, it just simply does not work anymore.

Whenever you buy information you are diluting its value by being another person using the same thing. And it's an endless game of trying to find the next thing. Some call it shiny object syndrome.

So what is the answer? I am not saying you cannot learn from information and get value. I am simply implying that it’s not going to give you a massive jump in growth.

You need to get into systems and processes that become more valuable with your participation not less.

What if you could access and contribute to the collective knowledge of what was working in your niche? The ads, landing pages, and audiences working the best? That would be cool, but not quite enough.

The future is having targeting that none of your competitors have. The ability to identify and collect the most accurate prediction of who your next clients would be.

I am not selling a course, training, consulting, or coaching. I am going to show you a software ecosystem that is going to disrupt and change how you market digitally.

With machine learning and artificial intelligence, it’s not even a fair fight.

Here is what you are going to learn.

How to cut your CPC 25-75% without changing ads or landing pages.

How to pluck the most qualified leads out of a local market.

How to position data in your offering to get clients begging to work with you.

Check it out -> https://www.agencygrowthsecrets.com/data

message:
Usually if you read this means, that you are a successful biz-owner and you know, that you aren't working enough ON your company, but instead to much IN it. That was me and my clients last year! We made a little change and solved the problem
You can learn right here in this text, what you need to see different, to solve your problem with hiring too. (And not just that.) The only thing you need to do is, to read until the end.
It doesn't matter if you are making 200 K a year o...r 80 Millions. Because the solution is the same for all and it is so simple, that you will find yourself thinking - why didn't I see this earlier!? But you will get that questions answered too in this text.
What I discovered over the past years, while creating revenue-increase-strategies with entrepreneurs is, that successful biz-owners are ambitious and driven and they want to do things by themselves. They are just used to.
They take help only after they tried by themselves. And those that don't, usually delegate the things, they aren't good at and when they hire, they hire to fill a gap or to fill some new discovered needs, in an area of their company.
They ask themselves, where do I find qualified staff? And if the company is bigger, they ask their HR department to search for it.
Then they flip back in their daily hamster-wheel and their overfilled to-do-list and run from appointment to appointment. To busy to find out, why it is like that.
Some even hire consultants, to understand whats going on, to support their staff and to understand how they can improve the different areas of their business. Just to discover, that this only adds more unclarity and confusion and even more tools, that their employees then struggle with. But certainly not, a feeling of clarity, control, simplicity and freedom.
What I learned with my clients is, that this is a normal state. It happens to all of us regularly. But, and thats crucial - a state has to pass. There has to follow a phase of clarity, freedom, settling down in the new areas, followed by more growth - revenue and ideal clients.
If we add valuable team-members, which support our companies growth and future-development, it has to be felt by our customers and seen on our companies-bank-statement. New employees can’t just fill a gap!
This is true for me and all 3 biz-owners I work with. Here a few examples:
Stefan, took the lead in the family biz lately. He is 3rd generation. That means a lot of clashes, between old and new structure. This happens a lot in fast growing healthy businesses. Stefan wanted to find qualified staff, especially to help his father to retire and therefore fill the gap that his dad will leave. At the same time, he needed someone, to that could support his plans for the business too.
Luca grew his event-furniture-franchise-biz from 0 to 250 K in 4 years and helped himself, with leasing-workers. The guys he got, where constantly ill and he could not rely on them, being there when he needed them. And so, his own hours summed up and when he was delivering a project, he hadn't even the time, to talk with his clients there to develop the relationships with them, for future sales and growth.
Andreas, real estate broker, simply grew his revenue very quickly. And then, he thought about adding team. But he also felt, only making more money, wasn't appealing enough. He wanted to build a company, that is more than just a money machine. So he needed the best, fast. (My own situation was similar.)
You may already guess the points. Its learning, that YOU are the center of all. ITS ABOUT YOU. About your goals and visions. And certainly not, reacting to situations or circumstances. Its about being active not reactive.
This clarity gives focus and focus attracts. It attracts the Best.
You become active and focused by answering these 3 questions:
Who is your ideal customer?
What products do they want and need and what do you really want to deliver?
And what do you need for your future growth?
If you want to dig deeper, you can schedule a strategy session right here. We get you a customised plan, that will be a true game-changer. http://bit.ly/sisesocasestudy
Andreas, hired his deputy managing director in only 3 weeks and he can also now choose more team-members, out of the best in the industry. Even CEOs that are in their companies since 10-20 years, show up on his door to work for him.
Luca, hired not just a fix employee after 2 weeks, but someone with the potential of becoming his future right hand and is on the way to his second employee, after having his best month since a year.
Stefan, hired a controller, that all his different departments and even the old and the new culture is happy with, in only 2 weeks, without advertisement or head-hunter. If you know Europe, then this fact is interesting. His new controller is from Switzerland, which usually is almost impossible to get, because of the salary-difference to Austria.
You want to provide the best value for your customers? Then get the best staff fast and easy. Apply for an in depth free conversation with me here: http://bit.ly/sisesocasestudy

Is that it is backed by the science of achievement...

message:
There are so many corporate engineers and managers who would LOVE to be their own boss but just don't know how (I've been there).

The simple answer lies in a Franchising model.

But there’s a lot more to it. There’s the worry of leaving the safety net of a 9-5. The struggle of knowing what to do first. And many people just don’t know if they have what it takes.

They want to be able to leave their corporate job soon. They want to be able to live life on their own terms and not driven by unrealistic deadlines. They want to be happy to go to work and enjoy time with family and friends.

That's why I set up “Job To Freedom Through Franchising”.

This FREE Facebook group is designed for corporate engineers, managers & anyone in corporate world who wants to:

- Get out of that feeling of being "stuck" forever
- Overcome the frustration of not knowing what to do
- Understand different business models and why franchising is the best option out there for them.
- Get clarity and feel confident about the next steps.

And above all, FINALLY start their own business, live life on their terms, have freedom and create beautiful memories, doing what they want, when they want.

“Those who cannot change their minds cannot change anything.” - George Bernard Shaw.

Come on in and embrace the change. CLICK HERE TO JOIN: http://bit.ly/2vnxAJo

message:
💥 Last Monday I launched something I'm very proud of...

✅ Something that will impact a lot of people...

📆 Literally more than 20 years in the making...

Designed to help Beginner Guitarists stop dreaming of the day...

They can play songs they love on the guitar…

And actually become the Guitar Player they’ve always dreamed about...

What my students find really amazing about this...

Is that it is backed by the science of achievement...

We apply scientifically proven strategies that take you beyond just having the desire to pick up your guitar, but actually start playing it and sounding great...

No more hemming and hawing about what to practice next...

And it all starts inside Play From Day 1™...

Imagine getting Monthly Action Plans (M.A.P.s), that hold your hand….

And take you step-by-step showing you exactly what videos to watch, what to practice, when to practice, and how to practice to get you playing the guitar as soon as tonight...

No more picking up your guitar and struggling with what you should be practicing…

You will have it all laid out in front of you so there is no second guessing yourself...

You get to turn playing the guitar into a game...

A game where you can visibly (and musically) see your progress as you make your way through my Guitar M.A.P.s

No more wasting your time scrolling through endless Youtube videos trying to find guitar lessons that may or may not help you...

My monthly action plans respect your time by providing you with the exact guitar videos you need to progress, in the right order, so you aren’t left trying to Frankenstein together the lessons from multiple instructors...

I've already had the pleasure of helping over 20,000 guitar players reach their true guitar playing potential...

The feedback is outstanding...

You might be thinking that something like this would be expensive...

But since I want to impact as many guitar players as possible...

Becoming a member costs less than a glazed donut per day...

And by signing up...

You get skin in the game....

And it gives me the ability to create a better, more meaningful experiences for you...

Check it out 👉 https://www.playfromday1.com/secret-sauce

🎸 PS: To sweeten the deal, when you become a Founding Member, I’ll even throw in my Barre Chords Bootcamp, one of my most popular trainings worth $138.97 to prep you for conquering Barre Chords in month 2.

PPS: Since I want to make the biggest impact on my members, this offer is only available to the first 500 people who join. After that, I may open it back up again one day, but I can't make any promises...

So if you know somebody who has always dreamed of playing the guitar but has never had the chance to realize their potential…

Do me a favour and leave a comment, or share this post.
Thanks so much and talk soon! :)

message:
Gay men are, frankly, people who have the same issues as everyone else: career dissatisfaction, family troubles, problems finding or sustaining intimate relationships, and concerns about health and aging. But…our community experiences them in unique ways with special considerations and opportunities.

Depending on a variety of family and personal factors, gay men come to adulthood with perhaps more questions than answers. Most often therapy is the route taken to get those ...questions answered. But is that really the RIGHT answer for you? Not that there’s anything wrong with therapy. If someone is depressed, bipolar, or in throws of an active addiction, then therapy is absolutely what is needed to handle what are essentially medical issues.

Otherwise, discussion, accountability, and resourcefulness around solving problems is enough so that each person can find their own answers.

I’ve recently started a Facebook group to create a forum for basically healthy gay men to discuss these issues and come to their own conclusions about what they need to get more out of life. In addition to the community discussion, I’ll be providing researched perspectives, articles, and ask the questions every gay man in mid-life needs to be asking themselves.

CLICK HERE TO JOIN THIS Facebook GROUP:

https://goo.gl/54oubQ

message:
When I was 19, I joined my university’s 6 AM ROTC physical fitness class as an elective. I was still a civilian, but I spent my mornings that semester working out with students who would go on to be officers in the military after they graduated.

One of the first things we did in that class was a 2-mile run for time. Our times were then used to sort us into groups for weekly runs; A Group was the fastest, E was the slowest.

I ran my two miles in about 14 minutes, which landed ...me in C Group. But since I wanted to challenge myself, I decided to start running with B Group instead.

The instructor let me do it, but warned me that I’d probably be bringing up the rear… and he was absolutely right. I lagged behind on every single run. Sometimes the group would crest a hill and I’d lose sight of them for a few seconds until I reached the top of it as well.

But even though I lagged behind, I still performed FAR better than I normally did when running on my own. Being in the company of far better runners helped me to mentally push myself, and I became a better runner as a result.

That was one of the experiences that taught me this lesson: The mind usually fails before the body does. And this applies to mentally taxing work as well - our internal motivation usually fails before our actual abilities are exhausted.

Want to combat this? Here’s one simple method: Be more positive-minded about your mental and physical endurance. Instead of telling yourself ahead of time that you’re probably going to get tired quickly, picture yourself as a person with above average endurance - and an above-average work ethic.

Sure, consistent habits and long-term discipline are crucial to actually becoming above-average in these areas. But becoming more positive about your level of endurance is something you can start doing today, and it will lead to a mindset that encourages those habit/discipline gains.
-
#selfdiscipline #mentaltoughness

message:
We love financial trading skeptics...

We love people who've realized that stocks are a 50/50 bet....

We love people who roll their eyes when they hear they can get rich quick...

We love it because we're those people.

And it's the story of how Sky View Trading began.

Take a moment to read our story here:

www.skyviewtrading.com/trial

If you've ever tried to make money off of just trading stocks, I think you'll be interested.

You'll hear of how I started in stocks, with a bit of money and a lot of hope.

You'll probably relate to my feelings of panic, terror and disappointment...

... to the feeling that every move I made was a "gamble".

That was back in 2009.

I now trade options for a full-time living.

And there's nothing particularly special about me -- my background or education.

I'm average Eli :)

If you go to our Facebook page, you'll see photos of me.

I grew up in a town of 3,600 people in the heart of Wisconsin (Go Pack Go).

I didn’t go to Harvard or MIT for college..

But I DID quit my six-figure career as a Network Engineer BECAUSE...

I found a trading strategy that allows me to CONSISTENTLY profit from the stock market.

In 2016, my business partner, Adam (better trader than me actually haha) and I started Sky View Trading together so we could teach these SAME strategies to other “normal” people looking to create a second income from trading.

So far, we’ve helped thousands of people do just that and we intend to help YOU do the same.

Trading profitably isn’t easy, because let’s face it…

If it were easy, EVERYONE would be doing it.

But it is DEFINITELY possible.

All it takes is a mentor (who has done it all before), a great strategy, and a lot of discipline.

I failed many times before I even started making any money.

But I learned A TON.

That’s why I’m here today…

I’d like to invite you to join our Free Trial to our Elite Membership here at Sky View Trading so we can begin helping you improve your trading.

Click here to get started:

www.skyviewtrading.com/trial

Here are just a few things you’re going to learn with our Membership:

✅ - How to add extreme consistency to your trading immediately.

✅ - Which strategies we use to consistently rake in profits from the market day in and day out.

✅ - How to trade without being glued to your computer so you can spend more time with friends and family.

✅ - How we profit in ANY market condition (up/down/sideways).

ANYONE can learn the strategies we teach.

I want to clear 1 quick thing up….THIS IS NOT A GET RICH QUICK SCHEME.

There is effort required not only from us, but YOU as well.

We are only looking for dedicated people to join who are serious about improving their trading and creating another stream of income through their trading.

Click here to begin your new trading immediately:

www.skyviewtrading.com/trial

My team and I sincerely look forward to working with you.

Eli

That's exactly what I told myself the last time I saw an ad on Facebook for a Social Media Course that was selling for $697.🤔

The ad was being promoted by a well known influencer (who I won't mention out of respect), and the pitch was good. 👍

The product was good too, he was telling people to start their own Social Media Marketing Agency - which is great advice. 👍

The reason I didn't like the promotion was because the price was WAY too expensive! 💲💲💲💲💲

I'm sure that the course was helpful, and many people ARE making a very nice living owning their own Web Marketing Agency.....BUT you don't need to charge someone 700 bucks to teach them! 😲😲😲

That's when I decided enough was enough.

You see, I own a web agency that did over $500K in the last 365 days. The best part is, I did it while travelling ✈️☀️🌊 for a quarter of the year. Thankfully, I am able to work from anywhere.

How is this possible?

One word.....OUTSOURCING.

By using outsourcing to help you run your web agency, you enjoy the profit that comes from selling high demand services to businesses, and you don't need to be an expert to do it.

✔ You don't need to be an SEO expert🔎
✔ You don't need to be a web marketing wiz 👨‍🔬

Outsourcing allows you to be an expert at anything, because you get other experts to do the work for you!

You still have to get your own clients and run a business, but when it comes time to delivering📦, outsourcing will get you there, without the heavy costs of full-time employees.

It's NEVER been a better time to start your own web marketing agency, and you don't have to pay $697 to do it.🤦‍

The Web Agency MasterClass explains you, step-by-step, how to start your own Web Agency and how I took mine from $0 - $500K. 🚀🚀🚀

You will learn EVERYTHING it takes to start and operate your own web agency selling web services to businesses.

In case your wondering, ZERO0️⃣ technical knowledge is required. 🚫

This program will teach you 👨‍🏫 everything from how to get new clients, to the best ways to deliver and keep your clients paying every month.

Now I'm sure you want to know how much this program costs.

I could have charged hundreds of dollars for this course, which is probably better than the one selling for $697. But I actually want to help people who need it, and I realize they can't pay $697 for a course.

That's why this course is just $39, for a limited time only.

Enroll now ➡ ➡ http://bit.ly/startagencynow

I don't know how long I'll be keeping it at this price, so take advantage while you still can.

P.S. I'm so confident you'll LOVE this program that I'll give you 60 days to try it out and will refund 100% of your money back if you aren't blown away!

message:
I won't post a picture of my private jet because I don't own one.

I won’t post any photos of my Lambo because I don't have one.

I wouldn’t post those pics even if I did …… because I am not like that.

My name is Eli,
I am a regular guy that figured out how to make a living trading Options Spreads. I also teach those wanting to learn how to trade options. I’ll get to that in a moment.

What are option spreads?

Option spreads allow us to profit even if we’re wrong about the direction of a stock!

The wins are NOT big and usually 10% to 15% per trade. However, The trades we place do have a high probability of winning. In using this strategy, we win 90% of the time. Yes, we post all our trades publicly for anyone to check out.

How do I make a living on 10-15% per trade? I trade multiple contracts at a time then consistently rinse and repeat hundreds of times throughout a year. I love trading options because it takes far less capital than stocks or any other “vehicle”.

About a year ago, I started teaching others how to trade option spreads and really got to experience how I can make a profound difference in someone’s life. Many no longer punch a clock for the “man” and are now full-time traders. Making this sort of difference in the world is the reason Sky View Trading exists.

Trading options is not for everyone. There is work and learning involved.

We break down the strategy in crystal clear detail and it’s up to you to watch, learn and ask questions. We’re with you every step of the way.

We’ll even tell you which contracts we’re trading and you are free to follow along. You can use paper trading (fake money) until you feel comfortable making real money trades.

For $14 you can test drive and see if trading options is right for you for 14 days. You’ll get unlimited access to ALL the training, trade alerts, and members area.

If you’re remotely interested in learning more, click here. https://skyviewtrading.com/trial

message:
💥 Last Monday I launched something I'm very proud of...

✅ Something that will impact a lot of people...

📆 Literally more than 20 years in the making...

Designed to help Beginner Guitarists stop dreaming of the day...

They can play songs they love on the guitar…

And actually become the Guitar Player they’ve always dreamed about...

What my students find really amazing about this...

Is that it is backed by the science of achievement...

We apply scientifically proven strategies that take you beyond just having the desire to pick up your guitar, but actually start playing it and sounding great...

No more hemming and hawing about what to practice next...

And it all starts inside Play From Day 1™...

Imagine getting Monthly Action Plans (M.A.P.s), that hold your hand….

And take you step-by-step showing you exactly what videos to watch, what to practice, when to practice, and how to practice to get you playing the guitar as soon as tonight...

No more picking up your guitar and struggling with what you should be practicing…

You will have it all laid out in front of you so there is no second guessing yourself...

You get to turn playing the guitar into a game...

A game where you can visibly (and musically) see your progress as you make your way through my Guitar M.A.P.s

No more wasting your time scrolling through endless Youtube videos trying to find guitar lessons that may or may not help you...

My monthly action plans respect your time by providing you with the exact guitar videos you need to progress, in the right order, so you aren’t left trying to Frankenstein together the lessons from multiple instructors...

I've already had the pleasure of helping over 20,000 guitar players reach their true guitar playing potential...

The feedback is outstanding...

You might be thinking that something like this would be expensive...

But since I want to impact as many guitar players as possible...

Becoming a member costs less than a glazed donut per day...

And by signing up...

You get skin in the game....

And it gives me the ability to create a better, more meaningful experiences for you...

Check it out 👉 https://www.playfromday1.com/secret-sauce

🎸 PS: To sweeten the deal, when you become a Founding Member, I’ll even throw in my Barre Chords Bootcamp, one of my most popular trainings worth $138.97 to prep you for conquering Barre Chords in month 2.

PPS: Since I want to make the biggest impact on my members, this offer is only available to the first 500 people who join. After that, I may open it back up again one day, but I can't make any promises...

So if you know somebody who has always dreamed of playing the guitar but has never had the chance to realize their potential…

Do me a favour and leave a comment, or share this post.
Thanks so much and talk soon! :)

message:
How A 23 Year Old Punk Started A Consulting Business From His Parents Garage In New Zealand, Moved To Manhattan And Made Forbes List in Less Than 5 Years!

I'm 28 now.

A little more humble than I used to be...

I've learned a few things on my journey I'd like to share.

Five years ago I was dead broke living and working out of my parents garage in New Zealand trying to start my own consulting business.

I cold called, door knocked, attended networking events and none of it worked for me. I was rejected, humiliated, forced to draw up proposals that nobody even looked at and ended up depressed with nothing to show for it but a $60,000 debt.

I didn't understand why the advice that was given to me in all of the books and all of the websites online didn't work.

My girlfriend left me because I couldn't even afford to take her out to dinner.

I worked 15 hours a day stressed out of my mind with a pay grade lower than a 16 year old on his first day at McDonald's.

I tried everything to get clients and none of it worked. Then one day I thought to myself:

"Instead of begging people for 5-minutes of their time and going to them, what if there was a way to make them come to me instead?".

I went back to the drawing board and stayed up days and nights on end figuring out ways where I could completely flip the model and make clients come to me instead.

Then one day i figured it out!

I went to work applying this new method for attracting and winning high value clients and it worked like magic.

1 client, 2 clients, 3 clients and then it caught fire and I had more clients than I could possibly handle and had to actually STOP marketing so I could catch up on the work.

Over the next 12 months I hit the 6-figure sales mark. Two years later, I hit the 7-figure mark.

I moved out of my parents garage in New Zealand and moved to a 28th floor apartment in Manhattan. I'm from a poor family in a small suburb in New Zealand...this was unheard of.

In Manhattan, things took off beyond what I even thought possible.

People started noticing my results and talking about my story and before long I had people asking me to teach them how to start their own consulting businesses and get high paying clients of their own.

At first I said "No" because I honestly didn't believe that anybody else could do what I was doing.

I thought I was unique...that I had a special talent and that nobody else would be able to make it work.

My ego had grown as big as my business.

But this one guy Stanley just wouldn't stop bothering me!

He would email me 2-3 times per day telling me he wanted to learn my methods and that he was even willing to pay me.

After a few months of non-stop messages I gave in and decided to try teaching my methods to Stanley. I didn't even think it would work for him but he begged me to do it. We jumped on Skype calls twice per week and I taught him my process from start to finish.

Within three weeks I couldn't believe it... Stanley called and told me he got his first client.

"How much did you charge him?" I asked.

"$10,000!"

I almost fell off my chair!

That was even more than I was charging at the time.

In 3 weeks, Stanley went from knowing barely anything about business or consulting...

...to charging more than I ever had for a consulting client.

Did he just get lucky?

I was curious so I accepted five more people and showed them how to do it and then BAM - they started getting clients too!

Then I started working with more people, the groups grew from 10 to 20 to 30 and I kept teaching them my same methods and they kept getting results.

I was humbled. I wasn't so special or unique after all.

But I did have a special, unique method for getting high value clients.

A framework that I found worked for any kind of consultant (health, financial, hospitality, marketing, real estate, etc).

Fast forward to this current day and I've helped over 3,123 people quit their jobs and go full time into consulting.

(you can see all 3,123 of them here https://www.consulting.com/reviews).

It's honestly hard to believe how this happened so fast.

I went from being depressed and broke working out of my parents garage in New Zealand to becoming a successful 7-figure consultant in Manhattan...

...to revolutionizing the e-learning industry and growing my company Consulting.com into a cash cow that Forbes valued at $65,000,000.

So what is it about my consulting methods that are so darn good?

How have I created extreme liquid wealth for myself and my clients in such a short time?

Well it all comes down to relentless focus on 3 key things...

We live in an A.D.D. world where there is too much information and too many distractions.

While others have tried to do it all - I have tried to do less. In the modern world it's more about what your ignore rather than what you do.

While others burn themselves out trying to do 52 different things I focus on 3.

Want to know what these 3 key things are?

I put together a free training for you showing you *exactly* how I got started and grew my consulting business into the 6-figures that first year.

I literally pull back the curtain and reveal it all including the "3 Key Things" that have been the foundation of my success and my students success.

You can register here for free:- https://www.consulting.com/free-training

In this free training I show you step-by-step how to get started, how to pick your niche, how to craft your consulting offer, how to get clients to come to you instead of you chasing them and more...

This isn't easy work. Even though people like Stanley get their first client in less than 3 weeks...it took me a little over 12 months before I made a single penny in consulting.

But I think my track record speaks for itself...

My consulting framework has created more full time consultants than anything or anyone I've ever known.

The lessons in this training are the bedrock of my success and my clients success and I'm sure they will serve you in the same way they have served us.

Register for this FREE training right now by clicking the link below.

Here's the link:- https://www.consulting.com/free-training

We only have a couple slots available so be sure to reserve your spot right now.
